UPDATE tour SET description = 'Venture to the wild end of the world on an epic trekking adventure through Patagonia''s breathtaking wilderness. Traverse the legendary trails of Torres del Paine National Park, walk beside colossal glaciers calving into turquoise lakes, and camp under some of the clearest skies on Earth. This challenging and deeply rewarding journey is a true test of spirit for dedicated outdoor adventurers.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b2-72a0-b456-0f635bb286e9';
