UPDATE tour SET description = 'Escape to the Seychelles, an archipelago of 115 granite islands draped in lush jungle and ringed by some of the world''s most pristine beaches. Snorkel over extraordinary coral reefs teeming with sea turtles and tropical fish, relax on powdery white sands, and explore the unique Vallée de Mai nature reserve. This island paradise is the ultimate destination for beach lovers and nature enthusiasts alike.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b2-734d-925b-0b02ca8f1c23';
UPDATE tour SET description = 'Enjoy the best of Mexico with an all-inclusive beach resort stay in Cancun combined with a fascinating excursion to ancient Mayan ruins. Relax by turquoise Caribbean waters, feast on unlimited gourmet cuisine, and explore the iconic archaeological sites of Chichén Itzá or Tulum. This effortless package perfectly balances sun-soaked beach indulgence with a rich cultural dive into pre-Columbian history.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b2-73a0-9dcd-392cfd887d05';
UPDATE tour SET description = 'Discover the regal heart of one of the world''s greatest cities on this curated London experience. Tour Buckingham Palace and the Tower of London, explore world-class museums including the British Museum and the National Gallery, and catch an evening performance in the legendary West End. From royal pageantry to cutting-edge culture, London rewards every curious traveler with depth, diversity, and drama.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b2-73b3-8a43-757b818c8062';
