UPDATE tour SET description = 'Sink into the laid-back rhythm of Phuket, Thailand''s most beloved island destination. Spend lazy days on world-famous beaches like Patong and Kata, explore colorful local markets, feast on authentic Thai cuisine, and take boat trips to nearby coral-fringed islands. Whether you''re after lively nightlife or peaceful seaside serenity, Phuket effortlessly delivers a week of warmth, flavor, and pure tropical pleasure.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b2-72f4-bbd9-20f6ad31b0ed';
UPDATE tour SET description = 'Fall in love with the City of Light on a perfectly curated Parisian weekend. Ascend the Eiffel Tower at dusk, explore the masterpieces of the Louvre, and stroll the chic boutiques of Le Marais. Savor croissants in pavement cafés, cruise the Seine by night, and soak up the effortless elegance that makes Paris the world''s most romanticized city. An escape that never fails to enchant.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b1-7c06-8e47-9df48d7e5028';
UPDATE tour SET description = 'Ski the slopes of one of the Alps'' most iconic resorts in the shadow of the majestic Matterhorn. Zermatt offers over 360 kilometers of immaculately groomed runs, car-free village charm, and a superb après-ski scene. Whether you''re a powder-chasing expert or an intermediate improving your technique, Zermatt''s exceptional infrastructure, reliable snow, and breathtaking scenery make every run absolutely memorable.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b2-7338-a261-74139c1b7af2';
UPDATE tour SET description = 'Experience the dazzling duality of Dubai, where futuristic skyscrapers tower over ancient desert sands. Ascend the Burj Khalifa, browse the vast Dubai Mall, and marvel at the choreographed Dubai Fountain. Then head into the desert for an exhilarating dune safari by 4x4, camel riding, and a traditional Bedouin camp dinner under a canopy of stars — all in one spectacular destination.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b2-71e7-ae79-d5a93d172b01';
UPDATE tour SET description = 'Set sail across the sparkling Aegean on a captivating cruise through the iconic Cyclades islands. Anchor at whitewashed Santorini, explore the windmills of Mykonos, and discover the ancient ruins of Delos. Swim in crystalline coves, dine on fresh seafood at harbor-side tavernas, and watch legendary Greek sunsets from the deck. This sailing journey is the most beautiful way to experience the Greek archipelago.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b2-724d-a31f-21ec6968bbe2';
