UPDATE tour SET description = 'Witness the raw power of Africa''s wildlife on an unforgettable Big Five safari across Kenya''s legendary game reserves. Track lions, elephants, leopards, rhinos, and buffaloes across the vast Maasai Mara, where the Great Migration is one of nature''s most spectacular events. Stay in luxury tented camps, enjoy expert ranger guidance, and return home transformed by the sheer scale and wonder of the African bush.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b2-714a-98a4-3553f18094c5';
UPDATE tour SET description = 'Dive into the vibrant energy of Barcelona, Catalonia''s sun-drenched capital. Marvel at Gaudí''s surreal masterpieces — the Sagrada Família, Park Güell, and Casa Batlló — before exploring the medieval Gothic Quarter''s winding lanes. Feast on world-class tapas and fresh seafood along the Barceloneta waterfront and experience the electric nightlife that makes Barcelona one of Europe''s most electrifying city destinations.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b2-7160-9329-cc7e8c3a8625';
UPDATE tour SET description = 'Journey through Jordan''s most spectacular landscapes, from the rose-red lost city of Petra — carved into sandstone cliffs by the ancient Nabataeans — to the sweeping silence of Wadi Rum''s Mars-like desert. Hike through the Siq, sleep beneath a billion stars in a Bedouin desert camp, and explore canyons carved by millennia of wind and time. A profound adventure for curious, intrepid travelers.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b2-7362-821a-a8eb904374ae';
