UPDATE tour SET description = 'Explore the soulful charm of Lisbon, Portugal''s hilly Atlantic capital, on a trip combining the city''s vibrant Alfama district, iconic yellow trams, and world-class pastéis de nata with a magical day trip to Sintra. Wander the fairy-tale palaces and Moorish castle of Sintra''s misty hilltops before returning to Lisbon''s waterfront for sunset over the Tagus — a perfectly balanced and deeply memorable Portuguese escape.' WHERE id = '019ee5e8-21b2-7277-909f-7c85b3ca612c';
